cu.explanation_en: Setting the ASN.1 verbosity to an unknown enum 'invalid' will cause configuration parsing errors and prevent the CU from starting properly.

du.explanation_en: Setting the CSI-RS enable flag to a negative value will cause invalid configuration and prevent proper channel state information processing.
du.explanation_zh: 將 CSI-RS 啟用旗標設定為負值會導致無效配置，並阻止正確的通道狀態資訊處理。
